WEBVTT

1
00:00:01.000 --> 00:00:05.500
Back to the Basics movement focuses
on rebuilding a solid foundation in life.

2
00:00:05.500 --> 00:00:10.000
Founded by George Bayze, it emphasizes
discipline, structure, gratitude,

3
00:00:10.000 --> 00:00:14.000
and personal responsibility
in a fast-paced world.

4
00:00:14.000 --> 00:00:18.500
The movement is built on three
core principles: guarded, grounded, and grateful.

5
00:00:18.500 --> 00:00:23.000
Being guarded means protecting your values,
while being grounded emphasizes

6
00:00:23.000 --> 00:00:27.000
living with discipline and clarity.

7
00:00:27.000 --> 00:00:31.500
Gratefulness reminds us that strength
without humility is meaningless.

8
00:00:31.500 --> 00:00:36.500
This movement aims to create men, families,
and leaders who are steady under pressure

9
00:00:36.500 --> 00:00:40.000
and intentional in their actions.

10
00:00:40.000 --> 00:00:44.000
Ultimately, Back to the Basics is a philosophy
designed to create lasting foundations

11
00:00:44.000 --> 00:00:47.000
that endure beyond our time.
